sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Publish as TopicDisplayer/BulkTopicDisplayer
    participant Manager as TopicManager
    participant Source as Source Topic
    participant Worker as ParallelAgent
    participant Agent
    participant Output as Output Topic

    Browser->>Publish: publish topic values
    Publish->>Manager: getTopic(source)
    Publish->>Source: publish(Message)
    Source->>Worker: callback(topic, message)
    Worker->>Worker: enqueue CallbackRequest
    Worker->>Agent: worker thread invokes callback
    Agent->>Output: publish(computed Message)
    Output-->>Manager: stores latest message
    Publish-->>Browser: topic table and refresh script
